<%= stylesheet_link_tag 'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap' %>

<div class="tiktok-auth-container">
  <div class="tiktok-auth-card">
    <div class="tiktok-logo">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="64">
        <path fill="#FF0050" d="M38.32 18.55c-3.04-1.67-5.11-4.34-5.7-7.56h4.4c.53 4.08 4.11 7.29 8.4 7.29v4.4c-2.99 0-5.72-1.27-7.7-3.33-.63-.64-1.16-1.37-1.6-2.15v13.2c0 7.16-5.8 12.96-12.96 12.96-7.16 0-12.96-5.8-12.96-12.96 0-7.16 5.8-12.96 12.96-12.96.87 0 1.72.09 2.55.26v4.56c-.82-.17-1.67-.26-2.55-.26-4.58 0-8.3 3.72-8.3 8.3 0 4.58 3.72 8.3 8.3 8.3 4.58 0 8.3-3.72 8.3-8.3V8.56h4.4c.53 4.08 4.11 7.29 8.4 7.29v4.4c-2.99 0-5.72-1.27-7.7-3.33z"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Autorizar Aplicativo no TikTok</h1>
    <p>Clique no botão abaixo para conceder permissões ao nosso aplicativo.</p>
    <div class="scopes">
      <h3>Permissões que serão solicitadas:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>✅ Informações do perfil</li>
        <li>✅ Listar vídeos</li>
        <li>✅ Estatísticas do usuário</li>
        <li>✅ Certificação de artista</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <%= link_to "Autorizar no TikTok", @auth_url, class: "tiktok-btn" %>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
body {
  font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f0f2f5;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  height: 100vh;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

.tiktok-auth-container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 500px;
  padding: 20px;
}

.tiktok-auth-card {
  background-color: white;
  border-radius: 12px;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  padding: 40px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.tiktok-auth-card:hover {
  transform: scale(1.02);
}

.tiktok-logo {
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

h1 {
  color: #161823;
  font-size: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

p {
  color: #606060;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.scopes {
  background-color: #f8f8f8;
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 15px;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.scopes h3 {
  color: #161823;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.scopes ul {
  list-style-type: none;
  padding: 0;
  text-align: left;
}

.scopes li {
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  color: #606060;
}

.tiktok-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  background-color: #FF0050;
  color: white;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
}

.tiktok-btn:hover {
  background-color: #FF2070;
  transform: scale(1.05);
}
</style>
